*[[빨갛다]] (''ppalgahda'') To be [[red]]
*[[노랗다]] (''norahda'') To be [[yellow]]
*[[하얗다]] (''hayahda'') To be [[white]]
*[[까맣다]] (''kkamahda'') To be [[black]]

